Module fi.tuni.roadwatch
Package fi.tuni.roadwatch

Class RoadWatchController

java.lang.Object
fi.tuni.roadwatch.RoadWatchController
public class RoadWatchController extends Object
This class controls the main UX components for the program. It contains the navigator bar and launches new fxml site's when navigator bar's icons are clicked.
